Photo shared by Draya Michele on July 21, 2021 tagging @kisharamarie, and @mintswimusa. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: Quick long story about @kisharamarie …. She made some cute bikinis and asked her followers to tag me because she wanted to work with me.(it worked) After looking at her page, I was surprised to see how truly talented she is.  So we did what any RESPECTABLE business would do…. We ADMIRED, then HIRED.  Kishara designed a one piece, a string bikini, And a skirt for this upcoming release of @mintswimusa …. We are honored that she brought her talents to us and today we celebrate her!!!! I can’t wait for you all to see !!! It’s a goal of mine to make sure I send the elevator back down to young women who have the same dreams as I once did. GEORGIA y’all got one!!! #blackdesigners #mintswim #admirethenhire #smallbusiness

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Draya Michele on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and pool.

node.text: I’ve been super patient this summer.  I’m not ashamed to admit at some points I felt I worked harder on other brands than my own.  But I promise new HEAT by @mintswimusa is on the way 7/23 (I promise it’s on the way don’t hold me to the date tho). New styles by me and collaborations with new black creators are on the way.  New prints …. We call this one “sherbet” ..🍧🌊👙… I haven’t dropped a 20 piece collection in a long time friends and I promise it won’t disappoint. 😌 #mintswim #mintysummer
